🔹 Example 1

Find 25% of 240

Solution

25%

= 1/4

1/4 × 240

= 60

✅ Answer = 60


---

🔹 Example 2

A student scored 72 marks out of 90.

Find the percentage.

Percentage

= (72/90) × 100

= 80%

✅ Answer = 80%


---

🔹 Example 3

30 is what percent of 120?

Percentage

= (30/120) × 100

= 25%

✅ Answer = 25%


---

🔹 Example 4

40% of a number is 80.

Find the number.

Number

= (80 × 100)/40

= 200

✅ Answer = 200


---

🔹 Example 5

Convert 3/5 into a percentage.

Percentage

= (3/5) × 100

= 60%

✅ Answer = 60%


